        <div xml:id="TK1123">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>karumaṇiyiṉ pāvāy! nī pōtāy-yām vīḻum</l>
<l>tirunutaṟku illai, iṭam!</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O you image in the pupil (of my eye)! depart there is no room for (my) fair-browed beloved.</l>
            </lg>
